Go Bold with @trysugar ♥️🌹
latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Received this super hamper from @trysugar. I loved each and every product , the lipstick being my favorite.😛
I have created this bold look using all the products that I've received and i loved how it turned out. 
Products that I've used here are
• Stroke Of Genius- Heavy Duty Kohl(06 Blue Skies)
• Face FWD- Highlighter Stick ( 01 Champagne Champion)
•Face FWD- Blush Stick (03 Mauve Marvel)
• Matte Attack Transferproof Lipstick (06 Spring Crimson.) I personally enjoyed so much creating this look.
If you want to create such bold avatars get your sugar products and enjoy experimenting different bold looks.
